  "notes": [
    "This configuration resolves current City of Scottsdale zoning by coordinate.",
    "full_zoning is preferred because it preserves the complete published zoning designation, including applicable planned-development or overlay designations.",
    "comparable_zoning is the City's simplified comparable or base zoning designation and does not replace the complete full_zoning value.",
    "The Scottsdale zoning layer does not publish a zoning-description, case-number, ordinance-number, historic, or transit-oriented-development attribute.",
    "The City states that its zoning information is provided for general informational purposes and does not warrant its accuracy, completeness, or suitability for any purpose.",
    "A resolved zoning result supports permit research but does not replace review of the Scottsdale Zoning Ordinance, applicable zoning cases, overlays, stipulations, or confirmation by the City of Scottsdale."
